<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1030802-anybody-ever-wonder-why-the-word">Anybody ever wonder why the word &quot;seventeen&quot; is only used once in the original book—precisely on page 17, in the phrase &quot;nearly seventeen&quot; (precisely at the end of line 16)? And why this edition (like so many others) doesn&#39;t respect the form of the original book?</a>
</div>
