        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1082132577" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15381257580165953966">This is a great Calvinist, horror, thriller, detective story, melodrama. It will be a great delight to anyone interested in the history of either detective or horror fiction. Unfortunately, I do not fall into either category and so somewhat churlishly only give it three.<br/><br/>Add one or two stars to my rating if you think the genre itselfis interesting. Ian Rankin loved this book and I think he is a source that any crime fiction fan could trust.</span>

